name: Pooja Hegde
text:
I know you wanna empower women in India and sometimes u worry your not doing enough, but don’t forget that I’m one of those women you’ve ALREADY done that with. I hope everyone finds their Devika, coz this one is taken❤️ Here’s hoping that year is filled with insane love, 
(3/4)

name: Pooja Hegde
text:
She told me to stand up for myself. That’s how our friendship began and 22 years later she’s still one of my biggest cheerleaders. Happy Birthday to the BRAVEST girl I know..my warrior and “my person”.
(2/4)

name: Pooja Hegde
text:
22 years of friendship! We were tiny pups when we met. I was the under confident, quiet and inhibited child. She was the confident, sorted and free spirit one. We met on the school bus. I told her about the girls who were bullying me in my class.
